'''''Pumzi''''' ni film ngufi ya siyanse y'impimbano yo muri Kenya yanditswe kandi iyobowe na Wanuri Kahiu . Yerekanwe mu iserukiramuco rya sinema rya Sundance 2010 mu rwego rwa gahunda yayo nshya ya Afurika.    Uyu mushinga watewe inkunga  n’ikigega cy’ubuhanzi cya Changamoto, ndetse n’ikigo cya Goethe Institut na Focus Features . Kahiu yizeye kwagura bigufi muburyo bwuzuye.  Filime iri mucyongereza,  ariko umutwe ni [[Igiswahili]] bisobanuye"Umwuka". 

=== Afurika ===
Pumzi igwa cyane mubwoko bwa Africanfuturism . Irerekana uko ejo hazaza hazaba umuco (uherereye kumugabane wa Afrika) utuwe cyane nabirabura. Byongeye kandi, yakozwe na sitidiyo yo muri Afrika yepfo igizwe nitsinda ryabashinzwe gukora no kumenyekanisha uburyo bushya bwibintu ndangamuco biva mubihugu bya Afrika. ''Pumzi'' ihuza neza na motif ikunze kuboneka muri Africanfuturism , ariko ntibigarukiraho gusa, kuba hari ahantu nyaburanga hatagira uruhare runini rwamazi.
